{"tid":143191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍中將: 美國在台灣部署薩德之日,就是解放軍解放台灣之時！","createTime":"2017-03-04T12:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T16:06:04.000Z","uid":408,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9672a1005f1de52d3fa4ba9d6b684c05375cb8e7","tid":143191,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:10:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170304/19947001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170304%2F19947001&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=9b4c5572\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170304%2F19947001&h=b16e054c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170304/19947001</a><br />\n南韓因部署薩德反導彈系統（THAAD），而遭中國報復鬧得熱烘烘之際，解放軍中將、南京軍區前副司令員王洪光（圖）被問及美軍不排除在台灣部署薩德時，他停下腳步說：「他敢！我今天把話撂在這，美國在台灣部署薩德之日，就是解放軍解放台灣之時！」<br />\n昨日全國政協會議開幕，出席會議的解放軍中將王洪光，在會後在被問到如何看美軍不排除在台灣部署薩德的消息時，<span style=\"color: red;\">王說：「他敢！我今天把話撂在這，美國在台灣部署薩德之日，就是解放軍解放台灣之時！不光是薩德，包括F35之類的進攻性武器，他敢在台灣落地！」</span>此外，對於美國在台協會新址「或將派駐海軍陸戰隊」的消息，<span style=\"color: red;\">王說：「我勸他們最好不要駐，要不然蔡英文會非常被動，具體措施我現在不好說。」</span><br />\n<br />\n網民：直接打過去就是<br />\n王洪光的言論一出，內地網民一片叫好：「話很霸氣」、「中國就需要這樣對美國霸權的將軍」，也有人說「長痛不如短痛，直接打過去就是」。現年67歲的王洪光，其父為開國少將王建青，岳父則為前空軍政委、開國少將高厚良。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020e0fac2c02f26ca2f2814328f48a2db00e076a","tid":143191,"uid":8493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:13:01.000Z","msg":"打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d91ec281a62afe77fa0a02c2e9ba903c130c03","tid":143191,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd5bfef81ae9d502d9e7be50efb229e6b6a3fa3","tid":143191,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:14:25.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"4e8b31b3433ac8df66f575c69fd0a306323827c4","tid":143191,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:14:44.000Z","msg":"打左南泡未🤔"},{"pid":"13e76c2efb07fa043b5903c5399d68659a1ec03a","tid":143191,"uid":10538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:15:47.000Z","msg":"嗯嗯"},{"pid":"ae8df3ac279bcaf7c9f6a564e304bc8876d83a95","tid":143191,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:18:27.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc125d71ceb092a2861c63313cdca3ea9de4a621","tid":143191,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:25:24.000Z","msg":"霸氣係用黎形容講得出做得到d人，成日人得個講字的所謂霸氣係泡影幻象"},{"pid":"177fd57eceefad4968d564ddbbe26a68a1188b35","tid":143191,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:31:06.000Z","msg":"防衛系統又唔係古巴彈導危機果隻戰略彈道導彈, 支那根本無野好驚<br />\n偽共帝國主義唔係想擴張根本唔駛怕, 司馬昭之心路人皆見"},{"pid":"b312631527139491ba01aac838aa200d27390630","tid":143191,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:33:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>防衛系統又唔係古巴彈導危機果隻戰略彈道導彈, 支那根本無野好驚<br />\n偽共帝國主義唔係想擴張根本唔駛怕, 司馬昭之心路人皆見</blockquote><br />\n香港搞限奶令, 保護番自己既奶粉<br />\n<br />\nD中國人都發左顛咁怒屌香港啦"},{"pid":"8f9074aef5723f1ad18985dcf77381adc5a8d351","tid":143191,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:34:57.000Z","msg":"過到台灣海峽當你贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" cla